<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink359">
<l>arumporuḷ vēṭkaiya mākiniṟ ṟuṟantu</l>
<l>peruṅka latariṭaip pirinta kālait</l>
<l>tavanaṉi neṭiya vāyiṉa viṉiyē</l>
<l>yaṇiyiḻai yuḷḷiyām varutali</l>
<l>ṉaṇiya vāyiṉa curattiṭai yāṟē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>When we, driven by the desire for precious wealth,  </l>
<l>abandoned you and set out for the place where roads [wind through] massive rocks, </l>
<l>the paths through the wilderness were so long!  </l>
<l>But now, as we return, thinking about the girl adorned with jewels,  </l>
<l>they have grown short!  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
